snippet: The people were killed in unrest in Caracas on Wednesday, officials said, as thousands took to the streets of the capital in the largest antigovernment protest in months.
abstract: Venezuelan officials say at least two people have been killed in unrest in capital Caracas as thousands of people take to the streets in largest antigovernment protest in months.
lead_paragraph: The people were killed in unrest in Caracas on Wednesday, officials said, as thousands took to the streets of the capital in the largest antigovernment protest in months.

headline.main: Venezuela: At Least Two People Are Killed in Protests
headline.print_headline: Venezuela: At Least 2 Killed in Protests
